<template>
  <a-modal
    :title="title"
    :width="1300"
    :visible="visible"
    :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
    @ok="confirm"
    @cancel="cancel"
    destroyOnClose
    :okText="okText"
    cancelText="取消">


  </a-modal>
</template>

<script>
  import {getAction, postAction} from "../../../api/manage";
  import {JeecgListMixin} from '@/mixins/JeecgListMixin'
  import DictItemList from "../../system/DictItemList";


  export default {
    name: "nextUsers",
    mixins: [JeecgListMixin],
    components: {DictItemList},
    data() {
      return {
        title: '用户选择',
        okText: '确定',
        dataSource: [],
        visible: false,
        confirmLoading: false,

        urls: {
          departUsetQuery: '/oaBus/taskInAct/deptUsersQuery'
        }
      }
    },
    methods: {
      cancel() {
        //初始数据
        this.dataInit()
        this.$emit('close');
        this.visible = false;
      },
      dataInit() {
        this.selectionRows = []
        this.selectedRowKeys = []
      }
    },

  }
</script>

<style scoped lang="less">
  .box {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;

    .left {
      width: 30%;
    }

    .right {
      width: 69%;
      height: 400px;
      /*background: #dddddd;*/
      overflow-y: scroll;


      .box1 {
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: space-between;
        /*background: darkcyan;*/

        .rightRight {
          /*width: 90%;*/
          width: 400px;
          height: 120px;
          /*background: #fff;*/
          margin-right: 30px;
          margin-top: 10px;
          overflow-y: scroll;
        }
      }


    }

    .rightLeft {
      width: 5%;
    }


  }
</style>
